comments: Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a legal position and he is firming up over his right leg when the contact occurs with Conley (UTA) during the pick.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact to Morant's (MEM) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) and Mitchell (UTA) engage in incidental foot to foot contact after Mitchell dribbles the ball off of Gobert's (UTA) during his drive.
Conley (UTA) and Allen (MEM) briefly engage in marginal contact during the loose ball.
Brooks (MEM) places his hand against Mitchell's (UTA) body and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) extends two hands into Morant's (MEM) body and the contact affects his putback shot attempt near the rim.
Valanciunas (MEM) places his left arm against Gobert (UTA) during the rebound and marginal contact occurs as he briefly grasps his jersey.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact to Anderson's (MEM) arm that affects his ability to make the pass.
Brooks (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Anderson (MEM) make contact to Gobert (UTA) that affect his ability to control the rebound.

Replay review of the out-of-bounds violation on Memphis pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Gobert (UTA) causes the ball to go out of bounds and Memphis is given possession of the ball.
Gobert (UTA) legally contests Brooks' (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) places two hands on the ball as Conley (UTA) gathers the rebound and a held ball is correctly whistled.
